title: Beta
subTitle: After the death of his mother, Raju's father re-marries, but his stepmother is only after the family's money. When Raju eventually marries, his wife tries to make him realise what kind of woman his stepmother is.

title: Dil Kya Kare
subTitle: The parents of an adopted child face issues of love, betrayal and custody when their daughter's birth mother arrives.

title: A Daughter's Tale: Pankh
subTitle: Vidya moves out of her house after her in-laws ask her to abort her second unborn girl child. Years later, one of her daughters, who is an ace lawyer, decides to fight a case against her own father.

title: Samadhi
subTitle: Lakhan Singh gives up his life of crime when he falls in love and marries Champa. However, things take a turn when she falls sick and he is forced to become a criminal again.

title: Abhimaan
subTitle: Subir, a singer, encourages his wife, Uma, to pursue a singing career. However, things take a turn when she becomes more popular than him.

title: Xcuse Me
subTitle: Two meddling friends Bantu and Chantu join a hotel management programme in Goa by pretending to be the owner's nephew and his friend. While training, they expose many employees and guests as frauds.

title: Rajnigandha
subTitle: Deepa, a young woman, meets Sanjay and falls in love with him. But when she goes to Bombay to look for a job, the arrival of a former lover puts her in a quandary.

title: Dharam Veer
subTitle: Twin brothers separated at birth become best friends, unaware of their bond as siblings. The queen, their mother, becomes the uniting force as they set out to defeat their evil uncle.

title: Namak Halaal
subTitle: Arjun, a youngster, works at a hotel owned by Raja and serves him faithfully. However, when he learns about a plot to kill Raja, he decides to save him from harm at any cost.

title: Dil Jo Na Keh Saka
subTitle: Jay and Siya, friends since childhood, decide to part ways to pursue their ambitions. However, they discover their true feelings for each other when their paths cross years later.

title: Rishtey
subTitle: A man marries his lover and has a child with her against the wishes of her wealthy father. However, his scheming father-in-law ruins their marriage and leaves to care for his boy by himself.

title: Rishtey
subTitle: A man marries his lover and has a child with her against the wishes of her wealthy father. However, his scheming father-in-law ruins their marriage and leaves to care for his boy by himself.

title: Barah Aana
subTitle: Three roommates decide to solve their financial struggles by going down the path of crime and kidnapping people for small ransoms.

title: Sau Din Saas Ke
subTitle: Durga marries Prakash, unaware of his mother Bhawani Devi's dominating and abusive nature. She later insists on moving in with his family in order to teach Bhawani Devi a lesson.

title: Hum Hain Lajawab
subTitle: Returning from a foreign land, Pawan, a cold-hearted man, sets out to take his late brother's son back home. However, a string of events forces him to rethink his rigid principles.

title: Mera Faisla
subTitle: Raj wishes to marry Rati but faces humiliation from her father due to the stigma associated with his lineage. Soon, he decides to join the police force to restore his family's honour.

title: Luck
subTitle: Moussa, a mafia leader, gives a bunch of people an opportunity to earn a hefty amount by making them participate in a game of survival.

title: Raj Kumar
subTitle: Rajkumar's mother sets out to oppose his marriage after she finds out that he plans to marry the rival kingdom's princess.

title: International Crook
subTitle: Rajesh, the superintendent of the police, is happy to meet his old friend, Shekar, in Goa, unaware that he is a smuggler, who is involved in a spree of illegal activities.

title: Speed
subTitle: A woman is held captive by a group of kidnappers to compel her MI5 husband to exterminate the prime minister of the country.

title: Raja Hindustani
subTitle: Raja, a taxi driver, falls in love with Aarti, a rich girl and marries her against her parents' wishes. Later, her stepmother tries to create differences between the couple.

title: Ranbanka
subTitle: Rahul, an ordinary engineer, comes to Mathura with his wife and son. However, when a gangster gets attracted to his wife and forces her to marry him, he tries to find a way to stop his advances.

title: Ranbanka
subTitle: Rahul, an ordinary engineer, comes to Mathura with his wife and son. However, when a gangster gets attracted to his wife and forces her to marry him, he tries to find a way to stop his advances.

title: Aulad
subTitle: Believing his wife to be dead, Anand gives up his own child to Yashoda, who has lost her husband and her baby. However, he faces a dilemma when his wife returns.

title: Katha
subTitle: Rajaram, a middle-class clerk, is secretly in love with his neighbour, Sandhya, but is too shy to disclose his love. However, he is taken aback when his smooth-talking friend soon woos Sandhya.

title: Jaalsaaz
subTitle: After the murder of millionaire Ranjit Rai, his mistress Radha is apprehended by the police. Journalist Rakesh teams up with his friends and a skilled defence lawyer to uncover the truth.

title: Bhabhi
subTitle: A woman finds out her husband only married her to get revenge. However, she finds solace in her brother-in-law who helps her escape the abusive household.

title: Rocky
subTitle: After his father's death, a traumatised Rakesh is adopted by a Christian couple who rename him, Rocky. Years later, he realises his true identity and vows to avenge his father's murder.

title: Swarag Se Sunder
subTitle: Two brothers struggle to keep their family together as external forces like the younger brother's father-in-law try to break them apart.

title: Charanon Ki Saugandh
subTitle: After returning to his village, Ravi learns that the local farmers are being oppressed by a despotic landlord. Soon, he decides to contest the panchayat elections against the tyrant and put an end to his cruel rule.

title: Dance Dance
subTitle: Two siblings, Radha and Ramu, belong to a poor family. Their life takes an unexpected turn when a tragic incident leaves them orphaned.

title: Yudh
subTitle: A policeman sacrifices his life protecting Savitri and her twins from a gangster. Savitri raises the fallen officer's son as her twins, now separated, grow into a lawyer and a sniper.

title: Amar Akbar Anthony
subTitle: Three brothers, each raised in different religious households, reunite after many years in a chance encounter. They set out to take revenge on those responsible for separating them.
